        <div class="col col2">
            
            <div id="page-title">
    <h1>Charles L. Weber Appointed Professor Emeritus</h1>
</div><!-- Ends: #PAGE-TITLE -->            
            <div class="contentDetail layout-1col-wide clearfix">
        
    <div class="col main">
        <div class="contentDetail">
	<div class="contentDetailNews">
	<h5>Distinguished radar and communications technologist will continue his research in the Ming Hsieh Department of Electrical Engineering</h5>
<div class="noprint" align="right">
 <table align="right" cellpadding="5" cellspacing="0">
        <tr>
          <td valign="top">
<a href="https://twitter.com/share" class="twitter-share-button" data-via="USCViterbi">Tweet</a>
